OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FQatar has taken steps for  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgay fans' safety - Cleverly
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Qatar has taken "real steps" to ensure 
OL,6, the safety of gay fans attending the   
OL,7, World Cup, Foreign Secretary James     
OL,8, Cleverly has said.                     
OL,10,FMr Cleverley told the BBC he had had   
OL,11,F"difficult conversations" with Qatari  
OL,12,Fcounterparts and had been clear how    
OL,13,Fseriously the UK takes the issue.      
OL,15,FThe build-up to the tournament has seen
OL,16,Fconcerns raised over LGBT as well as   
OL,17,Fbroader human rights in Qatar.         
OL,19,FHomosexuality remains illegal under the
OL,20,Fcountry's laws.                        
